(1, 1, '2010-10-08 18:12:50', '2010-10-08 18:12:50', 'This is my first BLOG entry in www.jobbyktom.com. My friends have asked me for years why I don''t start one. Frankly I didn''t have the time.  I  wonder how other people find enough time to moderate a blog with daily  articles. Yet,  I''ve been thinking of starting my own , and  finally i  achieved it.\r\n\r\nI now realize that there is so much information that I come across that is truly useful and I don''t always have time to write an article.\r\n\r\nIn many cases the ideas don''t require an entire article anyway. Blogging seems to make a lot of sense as an actual time saver for me. Thanks for reading and I hope all my time and effort helps (or at least entertains) you on many levels.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\n\r\nJobby', 'First Blog!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'first_blog', '', '', '2010-10-20 13:45:01', '2010-10-20 13:45:01', '', 0, 'http://www.jobbyktom.com/blog/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(2, 1, '2010-10-08 18:12:50', '2010-10-08 18:12:50', '<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.jobbyktom.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/me.png"><a href="http://www.jobbyktom.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/me1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-23" title="me" src="http://www.jobbyktom.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/me1.png" alt="" width="950" height="350" /></a>\r\n</a>\r\n\r\nI am a Software Engineer who has Photography as a passion. 									On this website you can view my portfolio of images, learn a little more about me and the equipment I use.\r\n<h3>Memories on the frame</h3>\r\nIn this site I have showcased my work  under different categories like  Landscape,People,Nature,Animals,Abstract,Urban etc. 								   I like to change it often, so please take some time to browse  and see what’s new. 								   I like to describe my work as ‘memories on the frame’. 								   I hope that some of the images that you see will bring back  memories of places that you have visited so that you too can have a  little reminder of what I think is one of the most beautiful areas in  the world.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'About', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2010-10-13 09:46:05', '2010-10-13 09:46:05', '', 0, 'http://www.jobbyktom.com/blog/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
